      publication: `<p>🎯 <strong>Target: Nature / Nature Methods</strong>. AlphaFold-3 (Nature 2024) and ModelAngelo (Nature 2024) set the precedent. A unified cryo-EM density foundation model is a Nature main-journal candidate. Backup: Nature Methods.<br><strong>Team:</strong> 1 PI + 2-3 PhDs + 1 engineer. <strong>Timeline:</strong> 12-18 months end-to-end; sub-projects can publish incrementally.</p>`,
