      approach_zh: `<p><strong>密度编码器 + 对比学习：</strong></p><ul><li>3D Transformer 把密度映射到 256 维 embedding</li><li>Domain-level encoding (via label_domain): each domain gets independent embedding (matching Merizo-search)</li><li>Positive pairs: same protein different EMDB entries OR simulated noise variants OR CATH-homologous entries</li><li>FAISS-indexed 55K embeddings → millisecond-latency search</li></ul><p><strong>跨空间对齐：</strong>把密度向量映射到 Foldseek 3Di 空间 —— 支持跨模态搜索。</p>`,
      key_challenges: `<p><strong>Challenge: EMDB has few "same-protein, multiple-entry" pairs for contrastive training:</strong><strong>Solution:</strong>(a) Data augmentation：resolution downsampling, noise injection, rotation;(b)  ChimeraX simulated maps as positive pair；(c) use PDB known CATH homologs as positive。</p>`,
